{{Administrative divisions of Laos}} [[Laos]] is divided into 16 [[Provinces of Laos|provinces]] ([[Lao alphabet|Lao]]: ແຂວງ, ''[[khoueng]]'') and 1 prefecture (''kampheng nakhon'') plus capital city municipality (ນະຄອນຫລວງ, ''[[nakhon]] luang''). Furthermore, 1 so-called special administrative zone (ເຂດພິເສດ, ''[[khet phiset]]'') existed between 1994 and 2006, when it was re-merged into its surrounding provinces (i.e. Vientiane and Xiangkhoang). Each province is subdivided into districts ([[Lao alphabet|Lao]]: ເມືອງ, ''[[mueang]]'') and then subdivided into villages ([[Lao alphabet|Lao]]: ບ້ານ, ''baan'').
