This is a '''list of mammals of the Marshall Islands'''. There is one land mammal, the [[Polynesian rat]]. There are 27 marine mammals, one of which has been classified as [[Vulnerable species|vulnerable]], the [[humpback whale]].<ref name=loc>[http://www.listofcountriesoftheworld.com/rm-animals.html]</ref>
==Marine mammals== The 27 marine animals consist mostly of whales, dolphins, and porpoises.
===Whales=== [[Image:A_spinner_dolphin_in_the_Red_Sea.jpg|thumb|[[Spinner dolphin]]]]
Whales include [[Humpback whales]], [[Ginkgo-toothed beaked whale]], [[Blainville's beaked whale]],<ref name=loc/> [[blue whale]], [[sei whale]], [[Fin whale]], and [[sperm whale]].<ref name=cause>[https://books.google.com/books?id=tjM0AQAAMAAJ&pg=SL265-PA23&lpg=SL265-PA23&dq=marshall+islands+house+sparrow&source=bl&ots=GcpLp90Ml4&sig=mQXghYI_3ytdozO64JHNOmBW3N4&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi12dvyh83TAhVB5iYKHSHfDq0Q6AEIOzAG#v=onepage&q=marshall%20islands%20house%20sparrow&f=false]</ref>
===Dolphins=== Dolphins include [[Spinner dolphin]], [[Fraser's dolphin]], [[Long-beaked common dolphin]], and [[Pygmy killer whale]].<ref name=loc/>
