'''WIPO ST.3''' is the [[World Intellectual Property Organization]] standard for the two-letter codes of countries and other organizations, such as regional intellectual-property organizations.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wipo.int/export/sites/www/standards/en/pdf/03-03-01.pdf|title=Two-letter codes for the representation of states, other entities and organizations|date=March 2011|accessdate=August 26, 2011}}</ref>  It generally follows [[ISO 3166-1]] except for the non-country entries.

== Current codes ==

Rows in blue are not present in [[ISO 3166-2]].  Rows in yellow are different from ISO 3166-2.  Codes AA, QM to QY, XA to XM, XO to XT, XW, XY, XZ and ZZ are available for individual or provisional use.

